   "source": [
    "As expected, k-means on the first 5 principal components yielded better fits. 3-cluster solution produced the silhouette width of 0.251 and adequate cluster sizes (11, 65, 60). Even though 7-cluster and 8-cluster solutions have slightly better silhouettes, we consider these solutions a little too extreme for a truly meaningful interpretation, because, once again, some of the clusters are of extremely small sizes. We therefore proceed with the 3-cluster k-means on the first 5 principal components as our final model for the interpretation. "
   ]
